OL,3,CJersey will vote on final assisted
OL,4,Cdying law in December
OL,6,FJersey will decide whether to
OL,7,Fofficially legalise assisted dying
OL,8,Flater this year.
OL,10,FThe draft law will be published in
OL,11,Fearly September before going through
OL,12,F14 weeks of political scrutiny, with a
OL,13,Ffinal debate and vote on Tuesday 9
OL,14,FDecember.
OL,16,FIf it passes, the legislation is
OL,17,Fexpected to come into force in 2027.
