OL,3,CJersey will vote on final assisted
OL,4,Cdying law in December
OL,6,FHealth Minister, Deputy Tom Binet,
OL,7,Fsays: "I think we're probably running
OL,8,Fa bit ahead of the game and I've been
OL,9,Fvery impressed throughout with the
OL,10,Fpeople that have been doing this.
OL,12,F"This could serve as a template for
OL,13,Fother places, it's that good."
OL,15,FPoliticians in Westminster recently
OL,16,Fpassed the next stage of their
OL,17,Fassisted dying bill covering England
OL,18,Fand Wales.
