OL,3,CJersey will vote on final assisted
OL,4,Cdying law in December
OL,6,FBritish MP Sarah Champion has been in
OL,7,FJersey to meet States Members and see
OL,8,Fhow they can support one another.
OL,10,FShe explains: "It's looking to see
OL,11,Fwhere our systems are similar, where
OL,12,Fwe can learn from each other and share
OL,13,Fexperiences, good and bad, so we don't
OL,14,Fmake the same mistakes."
OL,16,FJersey politicians backed the law
OL,17,Fchange to allow assisted dying in
OL,18,Fprinciple by 32 votes to 14 in May
OL,19,F2024.
