OL,3,CJersey will vote on final assisted
OL,4,Cdying law in December
OL,6,FIt would see those aged 18 or over and
OL,7,Fliving on the island for at least a
OL,8,Fyear given the choice to end their
OL,9,Flife with the help of medical
OL,10,Fprofessionals if they have a terminal
OL,11,Fillness and less than six months to
OL,12,Flive, or 12 months if they have a
OL,13,Fneurodegenerative condition.
OL,15,FFran Hall from the campaign group
OL,16,FDignity in Dying says: "Momentum for
OL,17,Fchange across the British Isles and
OL,18,Fbeyond is unstoppable and we're really
OL,19,Fgrateful that Jersey is leading this."
