OL,3,CJersey will vote on final assisted
OL,4,Cdying law in December
OL,6,FThis is an incredibly complicated
OL,7,Fissue and Jersey's Health Minister
OL,8,Fwants the States to have no excuse to
OL,9,Fsay no when the assisted dying draft
OL,10,Flaw is debated in December.
OL,12,FThe difference between Jersey and the
OL,13,FUK is that in Westminster, their law
OL,14,Fis being proposed by a single MP, Kim
OL,15,FLeadbeater, through a Private Members'
OL,16,FBill.
