OL,3,CJersey will vote on final assisted
OL,4,Cdying law in December
OL,6,FWhereas, Jersey's legislation is being
OL,7,Fput forward by the island's
OL,8,Fgovernment, making it more likely to
OL,9,Fbe approved as they have a majority in
OL,10,Fthe States Assembly.
OL,12,FHowever, this is still an incredibly
OL,13,Fdivisive topic and that is why Jersey
OL,14,Fpoliticians are so keen to talk about
OL,15,Fsafeguarding with other jurisdictions.
