OL,3,CJersey will vote on final assisted
OL,4,Cdying law in December
OL,6,FFor example, compared to the Isle of
OL,7,FMan, Jersey has different residency
OL,8,Frequirements, meaning someone could
OL,9,Flive in Jersey for a shorter amount of
OL,10,Ftime before being eligible for an
OL,11,Fassisted death.
OL,13,FWhat will be interesting is how
OL,14,FGuernsey reacts with a new set of
OL,15,Fpoliticians - could they soon be the
OL,16,Fnext place in the British Isles to
OL,17,Fpropose assisted dying legislation?
